channel.description:
[size=7pt]Sorry about the work you wanted me to do, see. Last night I was working on my website & I couldn't find out how to get the Pad BG in it so I could right on top of it. So I was really sleepy, it was about 4: 51 AM in the morning when I went to sleep last night... Sorry, will get on your work right away now.[/size]
[center][url=http://moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,163838.0.html][IMG]http://i14.tinypic.com/61yb1pw.png[/img][/url][/center] Currently: Open! =] Current Note: You may still post applications if were closed, still - Check out our website designs!
Made By: Jarod R Billingslea - Ted R Wickins Made with: •Gimp & Photoshop•
Welcome to Graphics Shop, We'll you make any picture you want for "free". It has been a while since we had ever made picture & now we've come back to regain the ability to gain your attention. Do not PM any of us for a picture (unless you need information on this company, pm me), you must come here for one because we would like this thread to be kept alive. Also taking in any member who wants to make graphics with us, our messenger contacts are
Legend: [i][b]Co Owner[/b][/i] | [u][b]Founder[/b][/u] | [i]Etc Artistes[/i] ¤ MSN Messenger: [b][u]Greek.Line@Hotmail.com[/u][/b] ¤Aim Messenger: [b][u]WildyNight[/u][/b] ¤Aim Messenger: [b][i]xTEDISNEATx[/i][/b]
The type of designs we do are your perfect need, we can make just about any signature you want anytime. The picture should be done within 2 hours are less depending on what type of signature you want layed out on it, meaning if you selected any strong signature - it would take us a while to do. Remember we do not charge you for anything except respect for what I am doing for you.
Pictures are custom made from us ONLY, you have to use our Application Template to order one:
If yo do not have the header of the application, we will turn it into a signature for you. We do not want you to mess around with your turn, so I would read this message if I were you. Your application should he like this:
